des:
Struggling with the right words? You are not alone.
Sending a romantic message to your loved one doesn’t always come easy.
We gather ideas for cute messages for your loved ones, so you don’t have to struggle with your own words when you really want to impress them.

Just say, 
Alexa, play cute messages
